column2: SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning, s.specClass, p.run, p.rerun, p.camCol, p.field, p.obj, str (p.ra, #, #) as ra, str (p.[dec], #, #) as dec, p.r FROM BESTDR7..SpecObj as s JOIN BESTDR7..PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id WHERE (p.type = # OR p.type = #) ORDER BY x.up_id
